<html lang="en">

  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="" />
    <meta name="author" content="" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="img/logo.svg" />
    <link href="css/generalStructure.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="css/bootstrap2.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="js/jquery-3.3.1.js"></script>
    <script src="js/bootstrap.js"></script>
    <script src="js/homepage.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN"
      crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>BigO!</title>
  </head>

  <body>

    <body id="page-top">
      <nav>
        <div class="navbar__item navbar__item--left">
          <button id="page-top" class="navbar__logo">
            <img class="clickable no-select" src="img/logo_com_nome.svg" alt="Logo BigO!" />
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="navbar__item navbar__item--right">
          <button class="navbar__button no-select" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signup">Cadastrar</button>
          <button class="button--call-to-action no-select" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signin">Entrar</button>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <main>
        <section class="hero">
          <h1 class="hero__title">Compartilhe conhecimento com a BigO!</h1>
          <button id="scroll-down">
            <img class="clickable no-select" src="img/down_arrow.svg" alt="Seta para baixo" />
          </button>
        </section>
        <div id="content" class="content-container">
          <section class="content">
            <div class="content__item">
              <h2>O que somos?</h2>
              <p>
                <strong>BigO!</strong> é uma startup que propõe criar uma plataforma que coloca <strong>
                  estudantes da área da computação no mesmo lugar para o compartilhamento de conhecimentos</strong>.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <img class="no-select" src="img/homepage-first-image.svg" alt="..." />
            </div>
          </section>
          <section class="content">
            <div>
              <img class="no-select" src="img/homepage-second-image.svg" alt="..." />
            </div>
            <div class="content__item">
              <h2>Conectividade para evoluir</h2>
              <p>
                Nossa plataforma permite que o usuário <strong>envie vídeos, links e outros arquivos</strong> sobre
                conteúdos relacionados à computação para que outros usuários do sistema possam ver.
              </p>
            </div>
          </section>
          <section class="content">
            <div class="content__item">
              <h2>Se junte à gente!</h2>
              <p>
                Cadastre-se e comece a <strong>compartilhar e receber conteúdos de seu interesse</strong>. A
                <strong>BigO!</strong> te ajuda a se formar mais rápido e com mais conexões!
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <img class="no-select" src="img/homepage-third-image.svg" alt="..." />
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </main>

      <form action="/save" method="post">
        <div id="signup" class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
          aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
              <div class="modal__header">
                <button data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                  <img src="img/close.svg" alt="Fechar tela de cadastro">
                </button>
              </div>
              <section class="modal__form-container">
                <h2>Bem-vindo!</h2>
                <div class="input-container">
                  <label for="name">Nome</label>
                  <input id="name" class="input--text" type="text" name="usuario_name" required>
                </div>
                <div class="input-container">
                  <label for="email">Email</label>
                  <input id="email" class="input--text" type="email" name="usuario_email" required>
                </div>
                <div class="input-container">
                  <label for="password">Senha</label>
                  <input id="password" class="input--text" type="password" name="usuario_senha" required>
                </div>
                <footer class="modal__form-footer">
                  <button class="button--call-to-action" type="submit">Cadastrar</button>
                </footer>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>

      <form action="/auth" method="post">
        <div id="signin" class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel"
          aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
              <div class="modal__header">
                <button data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                  <img src="img/close.svg" alt="Fechar tela de login">
                </button>
              </div>
              <section class="modal__form-container">
                <h2>Bem-vindo de volta!</h2>
                <div class="input-container">
                  <label for="email">Email</label>
                  <input id="email" class="input--text" type="email" name="usuario_email" required>
                </div>
                <div class="input-container">
                  <label for="password">Senha</label>
                  <input id="password" class="input--text" type="password" name="usuario_senha" required>
                </div>
                <footer class="modal__form-footer">
                  <button class="button--call-to-action" type="submit">Entrar</button>
                </footer>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </form>

    </body>
  </body>

</html>